verbose_text: The results also revealed that, compared with the H 2 O 2 and H 2 O 2 + NC groups, siNfr2 transfected cells treated with H 2 O 2 exhibited increased Bax and cleaved-caspase-3 expression levels; the protein expression levels of Bcl-2 were significantly decreased in the H 2 O 2 + siNrf2 group compared with the H 2 O 2 and H 2 O 2 + NC groups (XREF_FIG).
